<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200924/4575fb7b678d4c12ba4a3d645342f822.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">每年都要举办特色芒果文化节</span></img></p>
